export const stationTitle1 = "Margaret Smith";
export const stemText1 =
  "Margaret Smith is a 55 year old lady who has come in with a headache.";

  "where: one side, unilateral, at the back of the head",
  "when: one hour ago, recently",
  "quality: distressing thunderclap",
  "quantity, rate out of 10, severity: 10/10, worst in my life",
  "alleviating (relieving, better): none",
    "aggravating (exacerbating, worse): lights, photophobic, photophobia",
  "beliefs: none",
  "concerns: am I going to die?",
  "mother had autosomal polycystic kidney disease (renal disease, adpkd)",
  "family history/family hx: I'm not sure but if you specified some things...",
  "nausea",
  "vomiting",
  "neck stiff (neck stiffness)",
  "diplopia",
  "high blood pressure (hypertension, HTN), 150/80 today",
  "lost consciousness (loss of consciousness, loc) momentarily at start",
  "confused (confusion)",
  "smoke cigarettes 10 packs per day for past 20 years (smoked, smoking)",
  "occupation: primary school teacher",
  "eye movement/movements on looking to the left: left eye does not abduct"
];
